    <item>
      <title>债券交易员认为市场在通胀之前倾向于上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bond-traders-see-market-tilted-toward-gains-ahead-of-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国债投资者认为短期内上涨的空间大于损失的空间，因为预计美国通胀将显示经济的潜在价格增长正在放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bond-traders-see-market-tilted-toward-gains-ahead-of-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:06:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国在华企业称其受到当地人的不公平竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/german-firms-in-china-see-unfair-competition-from-local-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三分之二在华经营的德国公司表示，他们面临市场不公平竞争，这一问题可能会推高其成本并侵蚀利润率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/german-firms-in-china-see-unfair-competition-from-local-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管竞争对手因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎，宝马电动汽车销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马公司其核心品牌的全电动汽车销量在第一季度大幅增长，表现优于特斯拉和大众等竞争对手，后者一直在努力应对疲软的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国关键通胀数据公布之前，金价稳定在历史高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金价稳定在接近历史高位，投资者等待美国通胀数据，这可能有助于塑造美联储的利率前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 01:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
